<br>
It is still stuck at skill level 28 and holding steady. I cant find any definiteve guides to disarm at the moment so here are my questions:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 1) Can I raise the skill on non-weapon weilding animals?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
(IE: Mash Disarm when I fight animals)<br>
Right now I am fighting Zelniaks and stonegrabbers in Marus Seru that don't use weapons.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 2) Are there any tricks to Disarm?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
Using disarm when the special attack (eagle strike, tail rake etc.) is greyed out causes automatic failure?<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 3) Is it even a useful skill to bother with?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
I won't be surprised if monks neglect it, most warriors I know don't bother with it.<br>
<br>
Right now with 3 useful special attacks to raise skill on (Eagle Strike, Tail Rake and Flying kick), Instill doubt, Mend, Feign Death, disarm and with (relatively non-critical) sense heading / forage. Add to that, the &quot;pull&quot; message hotkeys, the &quot;mend up is up&quot; hotkey, the &quot;tag that pull&quot; hotkey I am feeling a bit like a monk bard with so many special skills and hotkeys to deal with. I am a relatively young monk, how do you guys deal with it <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ?<br>
<br>
Anyways - any thoughts on the Disarm skill is much appreciated. I just don't see my monk getting to fight that many armed creatures in Marus Seru (Recondos may have some though but I shudder thinking of raising such a skill on them). <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub38.ezboard.com/ussyxz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ssyxz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 57<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(5/7/02 1:27:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1483.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Disarm - useful monkly skill?</span><hr size=1> I refer you to this thread for all your Disarm questions: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub38.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showMessage?topicID=1456.topic">pub38.ezboard.com/fmonkly...1456.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
