Go to Field of Bone. Look for the Greater Scalebone skeletons who have the little rod in their hands (a magic bone weapon.) It helps to be high enough that it really can't hurt you.  Stand there and mash Disarm till you max.<br>
<br>
Since the weapon is magic, you can't disarm it but you still practice the skill...so you don't have to hand anything back to it.  I usually combine this on a button that disarms, FD, sits off, IDs and SH but you have to turn away so you don't actually ID or you have a chase on your hands. <p>in Service...<BR><BR><A HREF="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=109086">...Sauria Soulfarer</A> 39th scale Swifttail caste, New Sebilis<BR><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=222586>My Magelo</a><BR>Tolinu, 5th rank Ranger of Kelethin<BR>Furria, 5th tuft Shaman of Shar Vahl<BR>Laresa, 5th Note Bard of Kelethin<BR>The Order of Antondwer<BR>Guild Bankmistress with her Minions Ooabankone, Ooabanktoo and that harlot  Ooaraidbank<BR>Roleplaying on Vazaelle
