not entirely correct. it does not go up in skill if they are disarmed, but it does cause aggro, very low aggro. I pull with it all the time, as soon i get back to the group first person who hits it gets aggro since i have done no damage. Its great for pulling.  BTW anyone who only has a hot key for FK and no other special attacks... your really missing out on being a good damage dealer. Each one has a separate da/del. I can eagle strike 3 times in the timei can do 1 FK. If that was a missed FK or a hit for like 3 dam (the mininmu) i could have been better served with some tailed rakes or eagle strikes instead at 25+ a hit. It depends on the situation, they are basically different weapons, pick the dam/del to suit your needs at the given time. <p><center>
